## Parts comparison

| | Part 1 | Part 2 | Part 3 | Bonus |
|--|--------|--------|--------|-------|
| **Where Kubernetes runs** | VM (QEMU/KVM) | VM (QEMU/KVM) | Docker containers | Docker containers |
| **Number of nodes** | 2 (server + worker) | 1 | 2 (K3d) | 2 (K3d) |
| **Key tool** | Vagrant + K3s | Traefik Ingress | ArgoCD | ArgoCD + GitLab |
| **Where app config lives** | — | files in `confs/` | GitHub | GitLab inside the cluster |
| **Auto-updates** | no | no | yes (from GitHub) | yes (from local GitLab) |
| **Internet dependency** | for VM images | for VM images | for GitHub | no (after initial setup) |

